"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1931688-Teammate-rapist-Dutch-Olympian-making-best-Games\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The teammate of a Dutch Olympian previously convicted of raping a 12-year-old girl has claimed that the Netherlands' beach volleyball duo are \\\"making the best\\\" of their time at the Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20, \"end\": 25, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9642426108385553, \"rank\": 0.022458884583059675, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 26, \"end\": 34, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999984085258279, \"rank\": 1.589417943797918e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 106, \"end\": 117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7049133034703323, \"rank\": 0.41672386273544787, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Steven van de Velde's inclusion in the Netherlands team for the Paris spectacle has sparked major controversy due to his 2016 conviction.\", \"from\": 190, \"to\": 327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 197, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9994741149722153, \"rank\": 0.0005261617284689243, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}, {\"begin\": 229, \"end\": 240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7049133034703323, \"rank\": 0.41672386273544787, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 254, \"end\": 259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999927765887, \"rank\": 7.22341943415243e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The-29 year-old athlete served 13 months of his four-year prison sentence, leading to widespread questioning of the decision to allow him to compete in the French capital this summer.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 485, \"end\": 491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9984432094410326, \"rank\": 0.0013614670754564958, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde has chosen not to engage with the media during the Games and is staying in separate accommodation away from the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 638, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.1567823149599216e-17, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His participation has been met with boos and jeers throughout his time competing in Paris.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999927765887, \"rank\": 7.22341943415243e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite suffering two losses at the tournament so far, including a 2-0 defeat to Norway, and recording just one win, the Dutch have advanced to the last 16.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 868, \"end\": 873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9642426108385553, \"rank\": 0.022458884583059675, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, Van de Velde's teammate Matthew Immers has shared insights into the mood within the Netherlands camp, stating: \\\"We are making the best of it, and we are really happy at the end of the match.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7049133034703323, \"rank\": 0.41672386273544787, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us on Xfor the best and latest in sports news    \\\"So we said to each other, 'OK, did we enjoy this moment?'.\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We knew before the match we gave everything and we said to each other, 'Yes, we gave everything'.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's what we want to do every game, give everything and play our game.\\\"\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We lost the match, but we are second in the pool,\\\" he said, highlighting the team's standing at the Games as they prepare for the last 16.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was against the Norwegians, so we lost close.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9944890546143416, \"rank\": 0.005432423812697392, \"text\": \"Norwegians\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But overall, I think we played really good.\\\"\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After being convicted of rape in England at age 19, Van de Velde received a four-year prison sentence - but he only served 13 months before being released.\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9995862371122395, \"rank\": 0.00022830584623778448, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He served time in the Netherlands following a transfer and has been back in competitive beach volleyball since 2017.  International Olympic Committee spokesperson Mark Adams previously addressed the decision to allow Van de Velde to compete, stating: \\\"To characterise it as comfortable and happy would not be correct.\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1809, \"end\": 1820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7049133034703323, \"rank\": 0.41672386273544787, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q4760